</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="48C5FC04EC5BDC3DF0293F4E5D874A72" pageId="null" pageNumber="54" type="description">
<paragraph id="5F63950929C1CB7488942E0ADEF5DD7A" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">
<emphasis id="3447ACD6696718B0FD23D785438A6D16" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">
20-50 cm hoch. Rhizom meist ohne Faserschopf. 
<normalizedToken id="843066B113ABF7BE4B114EB45B7DECF6" originalValue="Blütendurchmesser" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Bluetendurchmesser</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="BDC8BB3FBC7458B2BC0C654C6F5DB40F" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">ueber</normalizedToken>
4 cm. 
<normalizedToken id="8D81DA5723E119BA3C43082F5E1FD465" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
innerseits 
<normalizedToken id="28B3DCAC3B0CF5B59014DA8600DBFA13" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">weiss</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, 
<normalizedToken id="306E2687146C5A8E1E4020D079607999" originalValue="außerseits" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">ausserseits</normalizedToken>
oft blau oder 
<normalizedToken id="E7981EE85C88FE7ADB14335BD9E565CA" originalValue="rötlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">roetlich</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="834F28AF14F7FF935FF25DFF45837DED" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Spitze der Griffel</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="8FB81DBBD0E29591621848FE424284D6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">ca. 1 mm lang</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="BE98E6129F8CE1728AA3C56E76E81A1A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">zur Fruchtzeit kahl.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="F878277826923363291F1D9377CA7EA4" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="342874252ADE334D592DD7F5974CC642" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="6BD4D161EC88B4B5FB08323DE7E8D7FC" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0219E9494726A2EE4DEE770ABECD4746" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">
<emphasis id="0CBCBCFA7D345EBD12C0B84E0F76805B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="45F336EDF29E1AF5DC6165EBE9D3FA5F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">16:</emphasis>
Material aus Liechtenstein (Rosenthal 1936), ohne Herkunftsangabe (Mattick in Tischler 1950, Aichele und Schwegler 1957), aus den Alpen und der Tschechoslowakei (Baumberger 1969).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D8698F3BDFA241AC9A95AE9A3DE1220A" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">
<emphasis id="D5610E13327FB0087B78975CC8C077FC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin, selten alpin. Kalkhaltige, trockene bis 
<normalizedToken id="E7AC5AA66BAFA2CAF6C93BEFB8AEEE01" originalValue="ständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">staendig</normalizedToken>
durchfeuchtete, steinige bis tonige 
<normalizedToken id="C1522F3A3DA6821135A2B917267AE6E0" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Weiden.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D524FD451E4E570B1054D7B2FC495C83" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">
<emphasis id="2890C6AAC5BF9A748B87ADDA42C99887" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="6D753386CAE2372F14D6119F172C9B8C" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze:
</emphasis>
Spanische Gebirge, 
<normalizedToken id="1ECCB6232C091051BE79E713BD85C7D1" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Cevennen, Jura, Alpen, Korsika, 
<normalizedToken id="0E6960FF96A7166460C809AC5C5CA3F5" originalValue="nördlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">noerdlicher</normalizedToken>
Apennin, Gebirge der Balkanhalbinsel, Karpaten, Kaukasus. Verbreitungskarte von Meusel (1965). - Im Gebiet: Alpen und Jura (
<normalizedToken id="AD1EECF8AEAEFBC8D799CF3DEF9E92EA" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Chasseral), stellenweise 
<normalizedToken id="5A0D50176B3EE46988D4E911EA362E68" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">haeufig</normalizedToken>
. Wo kalkhaltige und saure Gesteine sich 
<normalizedToken id="30F62F82DBB2013E00ADB5D8CEF48980" originalValue="berühren" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">beruehren</normalizedToken>
, kommen 
<taxonomicName id="22BD698E4D37E43AB76CED78C2930110" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Anemone" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="54" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="9E86EEFFD66D7DAD03B0EE03BA026834" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">P. alpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="B52224EDC3C4203CD38ED746713D4F0C" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Pulsatilla" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="54" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sulphurea">
<emphasis id="6B9D12D63CA39CEE060C10C4C85FDA53" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="54">P. sulphurea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1c) nebeneinander vor.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
